{"tid":1336302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"721中佬心聲","createTime":"2019-07-21T01:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T05:22:46.000Z","uid":276171,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"22daeb63567e4512bf951b82425a7f6ee364d5bb","tid":1336302,"uid":276171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T01:43:38.000Z","msg":"我是一個70後的中佬，父母前幾年已經返左天家，又一早決定唔會有小朋友，加上唔洗供樓，可以是最無負擔的一群！<br />\n今日是721，從這幾天很多新聞和消息，理性和直覺都話比我聽，今天會有好多事發生！但我不會怕，今日會繼續行出來，還會走到最前線，盡我力去保護年青人！畢竟依家這個困境，都是我這一代，掛住自己搵錢，無好好的為香港發聲，比中共有機可乘！<br />\n作為獨立抗爭者，今天已作了最壞的打算，如果真是不幸犧牲，靈堂上不用寫什麼英年早逝，只要寫著&lsquo;林鄭，我會返來搵你&rsquo;！<br />\n<br />\n寫在721早上"},{"pid":"c08389e62b899ecfde91046c7219089f3e70b77e","tid":1336302,"uid":70973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:09:34.000Z","msg":"be water<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7822efb6d2c20b93cd33a253d3c6357dd9dcaaf","tid":1336302,"uid":179414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:11:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊守護香港"},{"pid":"ea479479de97f3c8b92589079146b40bc72bacb7","tid":1336302,"uid":16372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcad9d9f35f1b43c7c8631645efb2739a283aa67","tid":1336302,"uid":17796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T05:22:46.000Z","msg":"一齊上，一齊走"}]}